This library allows you to use the open Web API Steam.

Overview

Create Steam client

Use only var

import steam

# input you Key Steam Web API
let keySteam = "XXXXYYYYZZZZDDDDAAAA1234"

# Create Steam session
var clientSteam = newSteamClient(keySteam)
